          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
        <div class="card h-100 shadow-sm">
          <img src="/images/Eve.png" class="card-img-top" alt="The Eve Mixtape">
          <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column">
            <h5 class="card-title">The Eve Mixtape — Vol. O.G.</h5>
            <p class="card-text flex-grow-1">
              The origin story redefined — rebirth, resilience, and rhythm.
            </p>
            <a href="/projects" class="btn btn-primary mt-auto">View Project</a>
          </div>
